                .container
                    h1.title.is-1
                        | Studying, #[span.has-text-weight-bold supercharged]. ðŸš€
                    h2.subtitle.is-4
                        | Level up your studying with Vocabustudy Pro and get access to all of our premium features.
                    .buttons
                        a#view-plans-btn.button.is-primary.is-large(href="#plans") View Plans
                        
        #plans.hero.is-large.is-bold(style="margin-left: -1rem; width: calc(100% + 2rem); padding: 2rem;")                 
            .pricing-table
                .pricing-plan
                    .plan-header Free
                    .plan-price #[span.plan-price-amount #[span.plan-price-currency $]0]/month
