            .message-header
                p Wondering which plan to get?
            .message-body After surveying countless students, our experts have deduced that the monthly price is roughly equivalent to the grades you will get in school!
        .hero.is-large.is-bold.is-warning(style="margin-left: -1rem; width: calc(100% + 2rem); padding: 1rem;")
            .hero-body
                .container
                    h1.title
                        | #[b Vocabustudy Pro] is the best way to study.
